channel.title: RSF2P [Remake]
channel.description:
So, I was inspired by The Unholy to start this ;). I love F2P, and always have, but we don't see enough of these types of servers no a days, nothing with F2P pking, skilling, and just overall f2pness :)
I will update this after every [b]big[/b] revision I make.
So far some features are: Magic (really unstable, no runes loaded for teleports) Melee Combat (going to re-write this later, due to I hate doing combat) Full F2P teleports Cannot use member teleports or prayers on F2P
Updates as of 6/2/2010:
[ul][*]Got the server base (deltascape) deleted a shitload of stuff [*]Worked on teleports and prayers [*]Found a new base client (temporary, need a blank 377) not silabs [*]Starting to re-write the magic system (spells, etc.) [*]Members items no longer load in the F2P client [*]Deleted all NPC spawns and shops, going to re-write all the F2P Npc and shops :p [*]^ Got 97% all F2P NPC spawns ^ [*]Added 80% F2P food (cakes, pizza, etc.) need to add the nooby ones, don't feel like it. [*]Fixed the scroll bar (thanks Kihomura) also need to fix the HP bar[/ul]
Updates as of 6/3/2010
[ul][*]Added base shops (axes, pickaxes, all that) [*]Fixed some spawns, and still working on them [*]Deleted all instances of member skills [*]Started to re-write the combat system [*]Added rune requirements for teleports[/ul]
Going to be working on today:
[ul][*]100% F2P spawns [*]Making P2P area inaccessible [*]Making 100% f2p shops [*]Going to work on the combat training (exp, mage exp, etc.)[/ul]
Media: [img]http://img576.imageshack.us/img576/3888/16233251.png[/img] [img]http://img202.imageshack.us/img202/1050/59105397.png[/img] [img]http://img214.imageshack.us/img214/7623/65888479.png[/img] [img]http://img408.imageshack.us/img408/2473/13169662.png[/img] [img]http://img99.imageshack.us/img99/2944/60224142.gif[/img] [img]http://img338.imageshack.us/img338/7028/83665075.png[/img]
I [b]MAY[/b] open this for others to help, not to sure though...
Also, need help with client sided stuff, and magic (spells etc.) so PM if you want to join (no noobs)
Anyways, post away, no flaming please :)
